data.label: Default customer location
data.tip: This option determines a customers default location. The MaxMind GeoLite Database will be periodically downloaded to your wp-content directory if using geolocation.

data.label: Enable taxes
data.tip: Rates will be configurable and taxes will be calculated during checkout.

data.label: Enable coupons
data.description: Enable the use of coupon codes
data.tip: Coupons can be applied from the cart and checkout pages.
When applying multiple coupons, apply the first coupon to the full price and the second coupon to the discounted price and so on.

data.label: Currency
data.description: This controls what currency prices are listed at in the catalog and which currency gateways will take payments in.
data.tip: This controls what currency prices are listed at in the catalog and which currency gateways will take payments in.

data.label: Currency position
data.description: This controls the position of the currency symbol.
data.tip: This controls the position of the currency symbol.

data.label: Thousand separator
data.description: This sets the thousand separator of displayed prices.

data.label: Decimal separator

data.label: Number of decimals
